# Volvo Grader Transmission Service Tender

## Title

* English: Request for Proposal: Volvo Grader Transmission Service (W0113-24CS11)
* French: Demande de propositions: Service de transmission pour niveleuse Volvo (W0113-24CS11)

## Reference Number
WS4413372961-Doc4413421766

## Tender Status
The tender has been cancelled.

## Procurement Details
=====================================

* **Procurement Category**: 
  * English: SRV 
  * French: SRV

* **Procurement Method**: 
  * English: Competitive - Open bidding 
  * French: Concurrentielle - Invitation ouverte à soumissionner

* **Selection Criteria**: 
  * English: Lowest Price
  * French: Prix le plus bas

* **Trade Agreements**:
  * English: *Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
  * French: *Accord de libre-échange canadien (ALEC)

## Contract Information
================================-----

* **Expected Contract Start Date**: 2024-03-01
* **Expected Contract End Date**: 2024-05-31

## Contact Information
======================

* **Procurement Contact Name**: 
  * English: Cheng, Sabrina
  * French: Cheng, Sabrina
* **Procurement Contact Email** : 
  * English: sabrina.cheng@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
  * French: sabrina.cheng@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca

## Tender Description
======================

The Department of National Defence requires a transmission service for two Volvo graders to be completed on or before March 28, 2024, with an optional three-year extended warranty. All submissions must be received by February 16, 2024, at 2:00 pm EST. Bids submitted after this time will be considered non-responsive. Please note that this tender was previously incorrectly posted with a different closing time.
